                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-102-off547 t18310630-102-cd548"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18310630-102-victim807" type="victimName">
                        Jonah Smith 
